## OVERALL VERDICT
Re-decide `overall_correctness` ("patch is correct" / "patch is incorrect") based on the priorities of the SURVIVING findings. "patch is correct" means no surviving blocking issue (no P0). Provide an `overall_explanation` and an `overall_confidence_score` that reflect the finalized findings, not the inputs.

